<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>三、杨洋狮驼号带队报名服战</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201109/3bc1ad2d2efc4307bf41a2a66126927f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
